Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:09.85,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}我也在去海邊兜風的時候對你一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:13.44,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}運転する横顔慣れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:13.44,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}習慣了你開車時的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:17.23,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}夏日的海風 清爽心怡的 Summer day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:17.23,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}潮風が気持ちいい Summer day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:20.36,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}LA LA LA SUMMER DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:20.36,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}LA LA LA SUMMER DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:23.91,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}ビッチバレーするカラフルなウェア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:23.91,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}沙灘排球時五顏六色的裝束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:27.62,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}砂浜に咲く花みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:27.62,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}就像在沙灘上綻開的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:29.87,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:29.87,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:33.29,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}あなたの心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:33.29,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}其實我真的好想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:37.63,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}もっと　もっと　近くに感じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:37.63,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}更近 更近的感受你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:40.42,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}私だけ見て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:40.42,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}請只注視著我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:43.80,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:43.80,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:54.31,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}服と膨らんだ胸の思い唇に乗せて伝えたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:54.31,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}好想將那滿脹的思念之情用雙唇傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.06,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}だから Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.06,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}所以要 Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:57.69,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}だから Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:57.69,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20}所以要 Kiss you
